Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:10.533 --> 00:00:19.499
Open facebook.com/share for Like Box code

00:00:19.500 --> 00:00:34.466
Click on 'Like Box' option on left side

00:00:34.466 --> 00:00:46.266
Lets start customizing our 'Facebook Like Box'

00:00:46.266 --> 00:01:01.232
Enter URL of your Facebook fanage

00:01:01.233 --> 00:01:10.533
Enter box width size as per your blog layout

00:01:10.533 --> 00:01:17.333
Enter box height size (its optional, you may skip)

00:01:17.333 --> 00:01:24.366
Check or uncheck Faces option (we keep it checked)

00:01:24.366 --> 00:01:31.166
Select dark or light color scheme, light looks good

00:01:31.166 --> 00:01:39.999
Check or uncheck 'Stream' option, we uncheck it

00:01:40.000 --> 00:02:05.866
Enter border color code like #dddddd or #eeeeee

00:02:05.866 --> 00:02:16.066
Then check or uncheck 'Show header', we uncheck it

00:02:16.066 --> 00:02:22.866
Neat Facebook Like Box is ready for use now

00:02:22.866 --> 00:02:28.999
Click 'Get Code' button

00:02:29.000 --> 00:02:39.433
Then click 'iframe' option &amp; copy the code

00:02:39.433 --> 00:02:53.266
Now open WordPress Dashboard &amp; goto 'Widgets' section

00:02:53.266 --> 00:03:03.932
Add new 'Text' widget to 'Main Sidebar' area

00:03:03.933 --> 00:03:12.099
Then paste the copied code of Facebook Like Box

00:03:12.100 --> 00:03:26.833
Click 'Save' button &amp; preview the Like box in action

00:03:26.833 --> 00:04:14.699
Play around with settings for different 'Facebook Like Box'

